title.narrative: Sustainability of the HIV Response in the Republic of Cuba

description.narrative: Cuba - HIV - United Nations Development Programme - UNDP Cuba. This program has the following goals: To reduce the incidence of HIV and STIs among key populations, with an emphasis on MSM.. The objectives of this program are: Fortalecer el acceso equitativo a paquetes de servicios integrales de VIH en un entorno de respeto a las diferentes orientaciones sexuales y la igualdad de género. Contribuir a la resiliencia y sostenibilidad del sistema de salud cubano
